dcterms:creator: Y. Labs
dcterms:description: The Yahoo Webscope anomaly detection benchmark supports real and synthetic univariate time-series problems for anomaly detection. It consists of a real dataset (A1 Benchmark) and three synthetic datasets (A2 Benchmark, A3 Benchmark, and A4 Benchmark) with 367 instances in total.
dcterms:title: Yahoo Webscope Anomaly Detection Benchmark
